metadata.name: R66 VINYL TOY // PRE-FORGED
metadata.description:
This toy is part of the first physical drop by R66 Space. 

Material: resin  
Height: 20 centimeters  
Painted: hand painted  
Packaging: yes

Please note that this is our first try on physical toys. 
All pieces were printed on 3D printers and hand painted by our team artist, therefore the toy may show small imperfections.

Comes in branded R66 Space packaging.  
By owning this NFT you have the right to claim a physical toy during forging event.
